text.text:
Jam gate is located in maheshwar about 50 km from Indore on mhow-mandaleshwar road. It's a popular picnic or tourist place. This arched gate has a roof with a platform on it. The view of the surroundings from its top is just amazing, especially in the rainy season.
Note - Be careful at the top of the gate, one should not step on the perrapet walls for selfies and all.

text.text: Excellent place to visit on weekends, you will love to eat Maggi there while sitting on khaat and viewing the beauty of nature at its best... It is on the way between Mhow-Khargone road, the road is well maintained and you will not have any issues in day time, but avoid driving at night because the turns are very sharp and dangerous and also you will be severely stuck there if your vehicle fails or punctures.... You are not going to get any help at the time of night because people also do not stop there.... Although your overall experience will be very good and also the Patalpaani Waterfalls are not very far from there, you must visit there also to utilise your whole day.... I visited there when I was going to Khargone from Dewas, it is greatly recommended to view the sunrise or sunset from the hill which will give you an auspicious experience and you will try to visit there every weekend.... Just follow some precautions and your trip will be very good, you should maintain the fuel in your car because you are not going to find any fuel station there and more problems come when you have a CNG vehicle.. overall experience was good, have a nice journey....

A beautiful place surrounded by nature's beauty at its very best.

100% recommended while visiting this area.

text.text: Nice place to spend time with family and friend.A place where you can really close to mother nature. A good spot to admire the nature and experience the sun set. The journey to this location is exciting in itself. You can visit this place with family and friends. There is no food or water service available here so bring that along with you. The place is peaceful and relaxing.Situated on edge of ghat having a very mesmerizing view. The road to this point is from ghats through lush greenery. A lot of Army and NCC camps are organized at this point for various activitiesas this place is very isolated and away from city and less crowded.
